Articles.Content:
Here are some highlights from my first Expedition to Eeloo. I just installed the Kethane Mod, and I'd thought I'd give it a try during my first trip to Eeloo. The plan is to have a unmanned Kethane Miner go to Eeloo first to prepare for my Kerbals arrival. The Kethane lander is accompanied by my standard Moon Tug.

Javascript is disabled. View full album
Congrats Sheer distance to Eeloo is always a challenge (to player's patience especially )
